@n_hoolywood has unveiled its Fall 2026 TEST PRODUCT EXCHANGE SERVICE collection, drawing inspiration from iconic U.S. military garments, including flight wear and ground crew uniforms. Reimagined through the lens of "supplying to the modern military," the lineup reconstructs classic pieces while preserving their original forms, details, and traditional material usage.⁠
⁠
Blending military heritage with contemporary functionality, the collection offers a modern take on enduring designs. Delivery of the collection will begin sequentially from June 27.⁠

@Hermes apre la sua sesta Maison al mondo a Londra, al 166 di #NewBondStreet: sei edifici, quasi 2.000 mq, oltre cinquecento opere d’arte selezionate sotto la supervisione di Pierre-Alexis Dumas. Il progetto, firmato da RDAI e Foster + Partners, unisce dettagli storici e contemporanei su cinque piani, con una scultura equestre firmata dall’artista #JessicaWetherly nell’atrio della boutique.
